text: Legendary. This was the start of a journey, every time you started the game, no matter which route, this would always greet you; a perfect opener, immense track, sets the fast pace of the game (for its era) and welcomes you into one of the best games you'll ever play. And I feel sorry for the young new gamers, ignorant to such genius of production, that they are born into an era where novel, original ideas are less favourable than sure-fire money-making sequels and film tie-ins. Legend game.
